### 2. Advanced Settings Features & App Version
We will introduce more administration and app configurations inside the Settings panel.

#### [MODIFY] [admin-settings.tsx](file:///c:/Users/PC/Fia-Cbt-main/fgsigbohocbtv1/client/src/pages/admin-settings.tsx)
- Add new settings options:
  - **Cheat Protection Warning:** Toggle switch to enforce window/tab switch alerts. (Local storage key: `fia_cbt_settings_cheat_protection`, default `true`).
  - **Global Passing Score Fallback:** Number input to configure fallback passing percentage (default `50`). (Local storage key: `fia_cbt_settings_passing_threshold`).
  - **Timer Warning Threshold:** Number input (in minutes) when the timer highlights in alert colors (default `5`). (Local storage key: `fia_cbt_settings_timer_warning`).
- Display a prominent section highlighting the **App Version (`V 5.7.4`)** with a clean, branded card layout.

#### [MODIFY] [exam-session.tsx](file:///c:/Users/PC/Fia-Cbt-main/fgsigbohocbtv1/client/src/pages/exam-session.tsx)
- Integrate the saved settings inside the active exam session:
  - Check `localStorage.getItem("fia_cbt_settings_cheat_protection")` inside the visibility change listener to optionally suppress or trigger malpractice alerts.
  - Dynamically check the `fia_cbt_settings_timer_warning` threshold value to highlight the timer countdown in red when remaining time falls below the specified minutes.

